		<td width="150" align="left" valign="top" class="row2"><span class="name"><a name="133592"></a><b>Petitioner</b></span><br /><span class="postdetails">Magician<br /><br /><br />Joined: 09 Mar 2003<br />Posts: 34<br /></span><br /></td>
