<br />
      So how exactly will any of this balance us with the other int classes? 
<br />
I see no balance here, i see slight mods to the allready crappy pets we have.  Its quite obvious that they do not want our pets to be any kind of actual defense for us.  When the pets they give us for a expansion cannot do the job of defending us in that expansion then there is something wrong.
<br />

